ons%20with%20a%20pugilistic%20mindset%20framed%20by%20the%20assumption%20that%20contractors%2C%20vendors%2C%20or%20other%20counterparties%20were%20overcharging%20or%20outmaneuvering%20them%20%E2%80%94%20or%20attempting%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20part%20of%20a%20smaller%20subset%20of%20landlords%20who%20took%20that%20a%20step%20further%20by%20freely%20renegotiating%20deals%20and%20contracts%20after%20the%20fact.%20He%20was%20also%20known%20as%20mercurial%20and%20combative%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20high-end%20real%20estate%20developers%2C%20high-quality%20real%20estate%20developers%2C%20didn't%20want%20to%20do%20joint%20ventures%20with%20him%20because%20of%20a%20reputation%20that%20if%20you%20had%20disagreement%20with%20him%2C%20then%20you're%20in%20a%20guerilla%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20attorney%20said.%20He%20was%20granted%20anonymity%20because%20of%20his%20client%20relationship%20with%20Trump%2C%20though%20he%20did%20not%20discuss%20specific%20business%20dealings%20or%20work%20that%20he%20had%20done%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20real%20estate%20lawyer%20who%20worked%20with%20Trump%20on%20a%20large%20retail%20lease%20in%20Manhattan%20also%20remembered%20him%20as%20characteristically%20unpredictable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20know%20where%20he%20is%20going%20to%20end%20up%20and%20what%20he's%20going%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20attorney%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%2C%20you%20can%20make%20some%20estimate%3A%20'I've%20dealt%20with%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20before.%20He%20is%20going%20to%20do%20this%3B%20he's%20going%20to%20do%20that.'%20I%20think%20Donald%20is%20harder%20to%20gauge%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%2C%20who%20also%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20avoid%20speaking%20publicly%20about%20a%20president%20who%20has%20shown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-said-hed-be-entitled-to-a-reven