ot%20of%20damage%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20his%20career%2C%20Mirante%20was%20the%20CEO%20of%20Cushman%20%26amp%3B%20Wakefield%2C%20which%20handled%20leasing%20work%20at%2040%20Wall%20Street%2C%20an%20office%20building%20in%20lower%20Manhattan%20owned%20by%20Trump's%20real%20estate%20firm%2C%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMirante%20said%20he%20remembered%20Trump%20for%20admirable%20qualities%2C%20such%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmaniacal%20attention%20to%20detail%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20punctuality.%20As%20a%20real%20estate%20executive%2C%20Trump%20would%20sometimes%20tour%20his%20buildings%20on%20the%20weekend%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe'd%20point%20out%20dirt%20in%20the%20corners%2C%20or%20he'd%20point%20out%20metal%20that%20hadn't%20been%20polished%20appropriately%2C%26quot%3B%20Mirante%20said%20of%20such%20visits%20to%2040%20Wall%20Street.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20a%20real%20asset%20when%20you're%20an%20investor%20and%20a%20developer%20and%20a%20buyer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20showed%20less%20focus%20on%20the%20homework%20that%20was%20sometimes%20necessary%20to%20evaluate%20the%20progress%20or%20strategy%20of%20a%20real%20estate%20investment%2C%20according%20to%20a%20real%20estate%20executive%20who%20co-owned%20property%20with%20him.%20The%20executive%20said%20Trump%20often%20wouldn't%20read%20investment%20updates%20and%20financial%20documents%20that%20were%20sent%20to%20him%20and%20was%20dim%20on%20the%20details%20until%20they%20were%20explained%20to%20him%20verbally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe'll%20call%20you%20up%20and%20go%20through%20it.%20He's%20a%20visual%20learner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20executive%20said.%20The%20person%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20identified%20disclosing%20private%20discussions%20he%20had%20had%20with%20Trump%20years%20ago.%20%26quot%3BHe%20wants%20to%20talk%20through%20things%20and%20explain%20things%2C%20and%20he%20gets%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20executive%20added.%20%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20he's%20a%20very%20confident%20guy%2C%20but%20he's%20not%20stupid%20by%20any%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20tendencies%20have%20carried%20over%20to%20his%20presidency.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-looks-at-charts-in-intelligence-briefings-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20famously%20didn't%20read%20intelligence%20briefings%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20first%20term.%20In%20Friday's%20argument%20with%20Zelenskyy%2C%20he%20sparred%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader%20over%20when%20Russia%20invaded%20Crimea%2C%20wrongly%20saying%20that%20it%20took%20place%20in%202015%20when%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20was%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1aa5384-9795-4b97-b6fa-092fd29c4dd1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFading%20optimism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20stoked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-office-interest-rates-risks-industrial-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidespread%20optimism%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20commercial%20real%20estate%20industry%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20White%20House%20with%20a%20pro-business%20agenda%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F01%2F23%2Fpresident-donald-trump-says-hell-demand-that-interest-rates-drop-immediately.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reduce%20regulation%2C%20and%20stoke%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20tapped%20real%20estate%20veterans%20to%20fill%20senior%20positions%20in%20his%20administration%2C%20including%20Steve%20Witkoff%2C%20his%20special%20envoy%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20a%20key%20official%20involved%20in%20negotiations%20with%20Russia%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoward-lutnick-real-estate-newmark-commerce-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHoward%20Lutnick%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20commerce%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20dizzying%20month%20of%20tariff%20actions%20and%20threats%2C%20an%20advancing%20plan%20to%20extend%20%244.5%20trillion%20of%20tax%20cuts%20for%20another%20decade%2C%20and%20a%20reordering%20of%20bedrock%20American%20alliances%20and%20policies%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20have%20raised%20worries%20for%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20and%20tax%20cuts%20could%20put%20upward%20pressure%20on%20long-term%20interest%20rates%2C%20which%20could%20hurt%20the%20health%20of%20the%20debt-dependent%20real%20estate%20business.%20Cooling%20relations%20with%20long-standing%20American%20allies%20like%20Canada%20and%20Europe%20and%20the%20embrace%20of%20adversaries%20like%20Russia%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20could%20influence%20global%20security%20and%20the%20flow%20of%20international%20investments%20that%20feed%20domestic%20economic%20activity%20and%20real%20estate%20dealmaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20real%20estate%20executive%20labeled%20Trump's%20decision-making%20on%20tariffs%20and%20tax%20cuts%20%26quot%3Bkamikaze%20economics.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20worried%20that%20prices%20could%20rise%20for%20steel%2C%20aluminum%2C%20and%20lumber%2C%20critical%20materials%20for%20real%20estate%20development.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20was%20concerned%20Trump's%20tax%20extension%20would%20increase%20the%20nation's%20%2436%20trillion%20debt%20and%20drive%20up%20long-term%20interest%20rates%2C%20which%20serve%20as%20the%20benchmark%20for%20most%20loans%20in%20the%20sector.%20The%20new%20administration's%20plans%20to%20deport%20millions%20of%20immigrants%20who%20do%20not%20have%20legal%20status%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20country%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20could%20affect%20the%20labor%20pool%20and%20push%20up%20wages%20and%20construction%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20super%20inflationary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%20firm%20Seyfarth%20Shaw%20recently%20released%20an%20annual%20sentiment%20survey%2