20ourselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-editor-mom-of-twins-shares-her-favorite-twin-products-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20parents%20of%20two%20newborns%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20once%2C%20we%20were%20completely%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShell-shocked%20and%20woefully%20inexperienced%2C%20it%20took%20all%20of%20our%20concentration%20and%20determination%20just%20to%20go%20to%20the%20local%20farmer's%20market%20as%20a%20foursome.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20hardly%20did%20any%20travel%20by%20air%20while%20the%20kids%20were%20toddlers%20under%202.%20That%20is%2C%20we%20grounded%20ourselves%20for%20the%20entire%20fleeting%20period%20in%20time%20when%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20required%20to%20buy%20the%20kids%20their%20own%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d14e58b1-e4aa-4223-a173-3c1db9c766f1%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20twins%20were%20young%2C%20we%20were%20just%20trying%20to%20get%20through%20each%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20definitely%20didn't%20do%20any%20air%20travel%20when%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwin-mom-cant-tell-babies-apart-tips-how-to-avoid-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwins%20were%20infants%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20thought%20parenting%20was%20so%20hard%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20it%20truly%20was.%20But%20looking%20back%20on%20it%2C%20those%20early%20months%2C%20before%20they%20could%20even%20crawl%20and%20were%20thus%20naturally%20more%20self-contained%2C%20now%20seem%20like%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20take%20them%20on%20long%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20didn't%20seem%20that%20way%20at%20the%20time.%20Frankly%2C%20just%20keeping%20them%20and%20ourselves%20alive%20was%20a%20tall%20enough%20order%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-approved-tips-for-traveling-with-kids-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20somewhere%20with%20our%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20somewhere%20far%20%E2%80%94%20seemed%20like%20advanced-level%20parenting%20that%20we%20were%20nowhere%20near%20ready%20for%20as%20bleary-eyed%20newbies%20with%20our%20hands%20and%20brains%20overfull.%20Nevermind%20all%20the%20gear%20that%20would%20have%20been%20required%20to%20make%20that%20happen%2C%20the%20thought%20alone%20of%20which%20was%20so%20exhausting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20those%20days%2C%20we%20frequently%20took%20them%20to%20a%20nearby%20park%20to%20watch%20the%20planes'%20thunderous%20landings%20at%20our%20home%20airport%20of%20LAX%20to%20get%20them%20excited%20about%20air%20travel.%20Happy%20as%20those%20memories%20are%20(and%20I%20think%20our%20strategy%20worked)%2C%20it%20wasn't%20the%20same%20as%20fanning%20out%20around%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20twins%20eating%20street%20food%20in%20Tokyo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c748a7b1834fe311661dd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20twins%20are%20now%20seasoned%20travelers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ed7fa75-b92d-4ff0-9882-e8585952003a%5C%22%3EI%20wish%20we'd%20started%20flying%20with%20them%20earlier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFlash%20forward%20a%20decade.%20Now%20that%20my%20kids%20are%2010%20and%20will%20soon%20wrap%20up%20elementary%20school%2C%20we've%20got%20the%20travel%20thing%20down%20like%20pros.%20They're%20seasoned%20travelers%20with%20fully%20stamped%20passports%20who%20know%20their%20way%20around%20a%20long-haul%20flight%2C%20a%20customs%20counter%2C%20and%20a%20subway%20map%20in%20another%20language.%20We%20are%20now%20living%20the%20exciting%2C%20rewarding%2C%20far-flung%20travel%20life%20I%20dreamed%20for%20us%20as%20a%20family%2C%20which%20had%20seemed%20so%20out%20of%20reach%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3