20savings%20of%20bigger%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a4f8adb-34e5-45b2-9ff0-4e16e827820e%5C%22%3ERumors%20and%20fears%20abound%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Trump's%20first%20day%20back%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20he%20issued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-first-day-immigration-executive-orders-deportations-border-visas-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20flurry%20of%20executive%20orders%3C%2Fa%3E%20pegged%20to%20immigration%20and%2C%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20promised%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20deportation%20program%20in%20American%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20November.%20However%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20deported%20in%20his%20first%20month%20in%20office%20was%20smaller%20than%20the%20monthly%20average%20of%20returns%20and%20removals%20from%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-set-broaden-arrests-deportation-routes-expand-immigration-crackdown-2025-02-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20isn't%20data%20on%20how%20the%20threat%20of%20ICE%20raids%20has%20affected%20businesses.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20threat%20of%20mass%20deportations%20has%20made%20some%20people%20who%20live%20in%20areas%20with%20strong%20immigrant%20populations%20afraid%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%2C%20Romain%20said.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20some%20of%20the%20fruit%20he%20sells%20is%20spoiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tight%20community%2C%20so%20if%20something%20happens%20down%20the%20road%2C%20somebody's%20gonna%20call%20somebody%2C%26quot%3B%20Romain%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20February%2C%20one%20of%20his%20customers%20told%20him%20she%20had%20been%20detained%20by%20an%20unmarked%20vehicle%20and%20asked%20to%20show%20her%20identification.%20%26quot%3BEven%20people%20that%20are%20documented%20a