%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20increased%20previously%20imposed%2010%20per%20cent%20levies%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20to%2020%20per%20cent.%20China%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20against%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States'%20unilateral%20tax%20measures%20seriously%20violate%20WTO%20rules%20and%20undermine%20the%20foundation%20of%20China-US%20economic%20and%20trade%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Beijing's%20commerce%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20imposing%20the%20tariffs%2C%20Trump%20accused%20China%20of%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20halt%20the%20trafficking%20of%20fentanyl%20and%20other%20highly%20potent%20opioids%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20has%20contested%20this.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fentanyl%20issue%20is%20a%20flimsy%20excuse%20to%20raise%20US%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports.%20The%20US%2C%20not%20anyone%20else%2C%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20%23FentanylCrisis%20inside%20the%20US.%20In%20the%20spirit%20of%20humanity%20and%20goodwill%20towards%20the%20American%20people%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20robust%20steps%20to%20assist%20the%20US%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20issue.%20Instead%20of%20recognizing%20our%20efforts%2C%20the%20US%20has%20sought%20to%20smear%20and%20shift%20blame%20to%20China%2C%20and%20is%20seeking%20to%20pressure%20and%20blackmail%20China%20with%20tariff%20hikes%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20been%20PUNISHING%20us%20for%20helping%20them.%20This%20is%20not%20going%20to%20solve%20the%20US's%20problem%20and%20will%20undermine%20our%20counternarcotics%20dialogue%20and%20cooperation.%20Intimidation%20does%20not%20scare%20us.%20Bullying%20does%20not%20work%20on%20us.%20Pressuring%2C%20coercion%20or%20threats%20are%20not%20the%20right%20way%20of%20dealing%20with%20China.%20Anyone%20using%20maximum%20pressure%20on%20China%20is%20picking%20the%20wrong%2