nch-this-week-125030500559_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDelimitation%20Based%20On%201971%20Census...%26quot%3B%3A%20Tamil%20Nadu%20All-Party%20Meet%20To%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmk-stalin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMK%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20led%20a%20meeting%20of%20state%20parties%20-%20including%20rivals%20AIADMK%20-%20to%20discuss%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fhindi-imposition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHindi%20imposition%3C%2Fa%3E'%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelimitation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelimitation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20topics%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20row%20between%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%20Mr%20Stalin%20tabled%20a%20resolution%20urging%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20ensure%20delimitation%2C%20if%20carried%20out%20now%2C%20is%20based%20on%201971%20population%20levels%20and%20retained%20for%20another%2030%20years%20to%20motivate%20other%20states%20to%20control%20growth.%20The%20resolution%20also%20sought%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20to%20ensure%20present%20proportional%20representation%20to%20all%20states%20if%20the%20number%20of%20MPs%20are%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20smaller%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20local%20ally%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Manila%20Congress%20(M)%2C%20did%20not%20attend.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20TMC%20(M)%20called%20the%20meeting%20a%20ploy%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20what%20it%20says%20is%20a%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Vijay's%20Tamilaga%20Vettri%20Kazhagam%20participated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDMK-Led%20Resolution%20On%20Delimitation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20also%20sought%20assurances%20that%20any%20increase%20in%20the%20total%20number%20of%20MPs%20will%20be%20calculated%20in%20the%20same%20proportion%20-%20MPs%20to%20states%20-%20as%20laid%20out%20based%20the%201971%20census%2C%20meaning%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20not%20be%20penalised%20for%20successfully%20controlled%20population%20between%20then%20and%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20encourage%20family%20planning%20by%20all%20states%2C%20in%202000%20the%20then-Prime%20Minister%20(the%20BJP's%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee)%20gave%20assurances%20that%20delimitation%20will%20be%20drafted%20based%20on%20the%201971%20census.%20Similarly%2C%20PM%20Modi%20should%20give%20an%20assurance%20the%20same%20draft%20will%20be%20followed%20from%202026%20for%2030%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTamil%20Nadu%20is%20not%20against%20delimitation.%20However%2C%20this%20meeting%20requests%20that%20delimitation%20shouldn't%20be%20punishment%20to%20a%20state%20that%20has%20implemented%20various%20social%20welfare%20schemes...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20also%20set%20out%20plans%20for%20a%20joint%20action%20committee%20-%20to%20be%20formed%20by%20MPs%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20other%20southern%20states%2C%20which%20have%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20delimitation%20-%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20awareness%20among%20the%20people%20about%20this%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelimitation-exercise-2026-lok-sabha-election-2029-mk-stalin-hindi-imposition-tamil-nadu-language-war-7790446%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSword%20Over%20South%20States%26quot%3B%3A%20MK%20Stalin%20On%20Delimitation%2C%20'Hindi%20Imposition'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20when%20he%20called%20for%20this%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20had%20warned%20the%20southern%20states%2C%