%20its%20%26quot%3BAnytime%20is%20Pepsi%20Time%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20taking%20direct%20aim%20at%20Coca-Cola's%20%26quot%3BHalf-Time%26quot%3B%20campaign%20for%20the%20ongoing%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20tournament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola's%20%26quot%3BHalf-Time%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20launched%20a%20month%20ago%20across%20TV%20and%20digital%20platforms%2C%20encourages%20consumers%20to%20enjoy%20a%20Coke%20during%20pause%20moments%2C%20such%20as%20half-time%20breaks%20during%20matches.%20But%20Pepsi%20flipped%20the%20script.%20Instead%20of%20waiting%20for%20%26quot%3Bhalf-time%2C%26quot%3B%20why%20not%20enjoy%20a%20Pepsi%20%26quot%3Bany%20time%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPepsi's%20move%20evoked%20nostalgia%20for%20its%201996%20%26quot%3BNothing%20Official%20About%20It%26quot%3B%20campaign%20starring%20cricket%20icons%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Vinod%20Kambli%2C%20and%20Mohammed%20Azharuddin%2C%20which%20cleverly%20took%20on%20Coca-Cola's%20official%20sponsorship%20of%20the%20cricket%20World%20Cup%20that%20year%2C%20jointly%20hosted%20by%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who%20remember%2C%20'Nothing%20Official%20About%20It'%20wasn't%20just%20a%20campaign%20-%20it%20was%20a%20cultural%20moment.%20A%20take%20from%20the%20brand%20that%20turned%20into%20an%20obsession%20amongst%20the%20audience%2C%20proving%20that%20sometimes%2C%20not%20trying%20too%20hard%20is%20exactly%20the%20winning%20move.%20And%20now%2C%20decades%20later%2C%20Pepsi%20seems%20to%20be%20channelling%20that%20same%20effortless%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PepsiCo%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rivalry%20between%20Coca-Cola%20and%20PepsiCo%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20in%20advertising%20history.%20The%20so-called%20'Cola%20Wars'%20peaked%20in%20the%201980s%20when%20Pepsi%20launched%20the%20%26quot%3BPepsi%20Challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20blind%20taste%20test%20showing%20consumers%20preferred%20Pepsi's%20sweeter%20taste%20over%20Coke.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20Coca-Cola%20to%20introduce%20%26quot%3BNew%20Coke%26quot%3B%20in%201985%20-%20a%20remaking%20that%20famously%20backfired%20when%20consumers%20demanded%20the%20return%20of%20the%20original%20formula%2C%20now%20branded%20as%20%26quot%3BCoca-Cola%20Classic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%2C%20which%20originated%20in%201886%2C%20was%20first%20sold%20by%20a%20pharmacist%20in%20Columbus%2C%20Georgia.%20Its%20original%20recipe%20included%20coca%20leaf%20extract%2C%20which%20contained%20small%20amounts%20of%20cocaine%20until%201929.%20Pepsi%20was%20invented%20in%201893%20by%20a%20North%20Carolina%20pharmacist%20and%20originally%20named%20%26quot%3BBrad's%20Drink%26quot%3B%20before%20rebranding%20as%20Pepsi-Cola%20in%201898.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741162440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-10%2Fpepsi-coca-cola_650x400_71475768722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpepsi-vs-coca-cola-cold-drink-war-returns-pepsi-vs-coca-cola-over-anytime-vs-half-time-7852712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20long-standing%20rivalry%20between%20beverage%20giants%20Coca-Cola%20and%20PepsiCo%20was%20reignited%20this%20year%20with%20a%20fresh%20advertising%20battle.%20PepsiCo%20recently%20launched%20its%20%26quot%3BAnytime%20is%20Pepsi%20Time%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20taking%20direct%20aim%20at%20Coca-Cola's%20%26quot%3BHalf-Time%26quot%3B%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpepsi-vs-coca-cola-cold-drink-war-returns-pepsi-vs-coca-cola-over-anytime-vs-half-time-7852712%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netizens%20wonder%20why%20Rekha%20ignored%20Akshay%20Kumar%20at%20an%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741162137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2F