ce%20(DRI)%20intercepted%20her%20and%20recovered%20gold%20bars%20worth%20Rs%2012%20crore%20she%20was%20allegedly%20smuggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ranya-rao-kannada-actor-arrested-on-gold-smuggling-charges-7851786%5C%22%3EThe%2033-year-old%20acto%3C%2Fa%3Er%2C%20who%20started%20her%20career%20with%202014%20Kannada%20film%20Maanikya%2C%20had%20flown%20in%20from%20Dubai%20on%20an%20Emirates%20flight%20on%20Monday.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20two%20people%20accompanying%20her%20were%20carrying%20the%20smuggled%20gold%20in%20briefcases.%20They%20had%20almost%20cleared%20security%20at%20the%20Kempegowda%20airport%20and%20were%20about%20to%20exit%20when%20a%20DRI%20team%2C%20which%20had%20specific%20intel%20about%20the%20smuggling%20attempt%2C%20stopped%20her%20and%20started%20a%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpon%20examination%2C%20gold%20bars%20weighing%2014.2%20kg%20were%20found%20ingeniously%20concealed%20on%20person.%20The%20contraband%2C%20valued%20at%20Rs%2012.56%20crore%20was%20seized%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Customs%20Act%2C%201962%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DRI%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20then%20moved%20to%20her%20home%20on%20Bengaluru's%20Lavelle%20Road%20and%20the%20investigators%20found%20more%20there.%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20interception%2C%20DRI%20officers%20conducted%20a%20search%20at%20her%20residential%20premises%20located%20at%20Lavelle%20Road%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20resides%20with%20her%20husband.%20The%20search%20resulted%20in%20the%20seizure%20of%20gold%20jewelry%20worth%20Rs.%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs.%202.67%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lady%20passenger%20has%20been%20placed%20under%20arrest%20under%20the%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Customs%20Act%2C%201962%20and%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody.%20The%20total%20seizure%20in%20