0cricketers%20of%20his%20generation%2C%20Australia%20batter%20Steve%20Smith%20has%20announced%20retirement%20from%20ODI%20cricket%20after%20the%20team's%20elimination%20from%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20on%20Tuesday.%20Smith%20was%20named%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20national%20team%20for%20the%20tournament%20after%20primary%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20was%20ruled%20out%20due%20to%20an%20injury.%20Smith%20led%20his%20troops%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20semi-final%20of%20the%20tournament%20before%20his%20team%20was%20eliminated%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%2C%20who%20retires%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prolific%20cricketers%20for%20Australia%20in%20the%20format%2C%20featured%20in%20a%20whopping%20170%20ODIs%20for%20the%20team%2C%20scoring%20572%20runs%20with%2012%20centuries%20while%20also%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20twice.%20However%2C%20the%20announcement%20means%20that%20Smith%20will%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Australian%20team%20in%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20a%20great%20ride%2C%20and%20I%20have%20loved%20every%20minute%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20so%20many%20amazing%20times%20and%20wonderful%20memories.%20Winning%20two%20World%20Cups%20was%20a%20great%20highlight%20along%20with%20the%20many%20fantastic%20team-mates%20who%20shared%20the%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20in%20a%20media%20release%20shared%20by%20Cricket%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20great%20Steve%20Smith%20has%20called%20time%20on%20a%20superb%20ODI%20career%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjsKDmVSG1h%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjsKDmVSG1h%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Cricket%20Australia%20(%40CricketAus)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCricketAus%2Fstatus%2F1897169001576534496%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Et