%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fin-2023-delhi-faced-flood-as-floodgates-were-closed-1300-tonnes-of-garbage-removed-from-yamuna-in-past-10-days-says-minister-parvesh-verma%2Farticleshow%2F118728086.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Biju%20Patnaik%20Has%20Become%20Latest%20BJP%20vs%20Opposition%20Flashpoint%20In%20Odisha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20hundred%20years%20after%20his%20birth%2C%20the%20legendary%20Odisha%20politician%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20birthday%20has%20become%20a%20political%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20party%2C%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD).%20The%20Odisha%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20delink%20the%20celebration%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Divas%20from%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Biju%20Patnaik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20has%20been%20met%20with%20strong%20opposition%20from%20both%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20who%20view%20it%20as%20an%20affront%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20Biju%20Patnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Biju%20Patnaik%20Is%20Celebrated%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%20March%205%2C%201916%20in%20Cuttack%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik%20belonged%20to%20a%20family%20rooted%20in%20India's%20freedom%20struggle.%20While%20his%20father%2C%20Lakshminarayan%20Patnaik%2C%20hailed%20from%20the%20literary%20and%20culturally%20rich%20village%20of%20Nuagaon%20in%20Ganjam%20district%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20Ashalata%20Devi%2C%20had%20an%20interesting%20subplot%20involving%20East%20Bengal.%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20maternal%20uncles%20were%20among%20the%20revolutionary%20youths%20responsible%20for%20the%20Chittagong%20Armoury%20Raid%20of%201930%2C%20along%20with%20Surya%20Sen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%20sixteen%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik%20got%20on%20a%20bicycle%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%202%2C385-kilometre%20journey%20from%20Cuttack%20to%20Peshawar%2C%20accompanied%20by%20friends%20Amar%20Dey%20and%20Bhramarbar%20Sahu.%20He%20would%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20in%201938%2C%20not%20on%20a%20cycle%20but%20with%20band%2C%20baaja%2C%20baraat%2C%20and%20a%20plane%20to%20marry%20Gyan%2C%20a%20Punjabi%20woman%20from%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20Patnaik's%20daredevil%20feats%20included%20flying%20missions%20during%20World%20War%20II%20with%20the%20Royal%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20and%20sheltering%20political%20dissidents%20like%20JP%20Narayan%2C%20RM%20Lohia%2C%20and%20Aruna%20Asaf%20Ali.%20During%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik%20dropped%20bags%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BQuit%20India%26quot%3B%20leaflets%20over%20Indian%20soldiers%20under%20British%20command.%20In%201943%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20clandestine%20double-life%20and%20covert%20activities%20caught%20up%20with%20him%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest%20and%20a%20two-year%20imprisonment.%20Upon%20his%20release%20in%201945%2C%20he%20entered%20politics%2C%20winning%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20Orissa%20Assembly%20from%20North%20Cuttack%20constituency%20in%201946.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru's%20trusted%20lieutenant%20back%20then%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik%20was%20tasked%20with%20rescuing%20Indonesian%20Prime%20Minister%20Sutan%20Sjahrir%20and%20Vice%20President%20Mohammad%20Hatta%20out%20of%20Java.%20Despite%20Dutch%20overwatch%20around%20the%20islands%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik%20rescued%20both%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20eventually%20went%20on%20to%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Odisha%20and%20upon%20his%20death%2C%20his%20son%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20carried%20his%20legacy%20forward%20by%20forming%20a%20party%20in%20his%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Happening%20Now%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20March%205%20has%20been%20observed%20as%20both%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20birth%20anniversary%20and%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Divas%20in%20Odisha.%20This%20practice%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20honoring%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20contributions%20to%20the%20state.%20In%201991%2C%20under%20his%20leadership%2C%20Odisha%20became%20the%20first%20state%20to%20reserve%20one-third%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20Panchayati%20Raj%20institutions%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20current%20administration%20has%20announced%20that%20while%20March%205%20will%20continue%20to%20commemorate%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Divas%20will%20be%20observed%20on%20April%2024%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20national%20celebration.%20Consequently%2C%20March%205%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20a%20public%20holiday%2C%20and%20all%20schools%20and%20government%20offices%20will%20remain%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20has%20been%20perceived%20by%20opposition%20parties%20as%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20diminish%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20legacy.%20BJD%20leaders%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20near%20the%20Biju%20Patnaik%20statue%20near%20the%20airport%20in%20Bhubaneswar.%20Senior%20BJD%20leaders%20expressed%20their%20frustration%20over%20the%20change%2C%20stressing%20that%20previous%20administrations%2C%20including%20those%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20had%20consistently%20celebrated%20March%205%20as%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Divas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20minister%20and%20Opposition%20Chief%20Whip%20Pramila%20Mallik%20praised%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20role%20in%20introducing%20the%20three-tier%20panchayat%20system%20in%20Odisha%20during%20his%20second%20term%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20in%201990.%20She%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20attempting%20to%20erase%20his%20relevance%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20condemned%20the%20move.%20Odisha%20Congress%20chief%20Bhakta%20Das%20alleged%20that%20the%20move%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20bury%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20legendary%20leader.%20Other%20senior%20Congress%20figures%2C%20including%20Jaydev%20Jena%2C%20Taraprasad%20Bahinipati%2C%20and%20Jagannath%20Patnaik%2C%20echoed%20these%20sentiments%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20deliberately%20insulting%20Biju%20Patnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Odisha%20BJP%20defended%20the%20decision%2C%20noting%20that%20April%2024%20is%20nationally%20recognised%20as%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Day%2C%20marking%20the%20constitutional%20recognition%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Raj%20system%20through%20the%2073rd%20Amendment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Odisha%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20its%20history%20by%20handing%20a%20shock%20defeat%20to%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20and%20his%20party%20in%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20refuted%20allegations%20of%20disrespect%20towards%20Biju%20Patnaik%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20birth%20anniversaries%20of%20other%20former%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20such%20as%20Harekrushna%20Mahatab%20and%20Janaki%20Ballabh%20Pattnaik%2C%20are%20also%20commemorated%20at%20the%20government%20level.%20The%20BJP%20has%20questioned%20why%20the%20BJD%20had%20previously%20overlooked%20these%20leaders%20while%20honoring%20Biju%20Patnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20assuming%20power%20in%202024%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20renamed%2021%20state%20schemes%20initially%20launched%20by%20the%20BJD%20administration%2C%20several%20of%20which%20bore%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happens%20Next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%20over%20the%20change%2C%20Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Majhi%20has%20invited%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20to%20attend%20the%20state-level%20function%20to%20commemorate%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20birthday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20humble%20respect%20to%20you.%20The%20State%20government%20is%20celebrating%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20great%20son%20of%20Odisha%2C%20the%20legendary%20Biju%20Patnaik.%20A%20state-level%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20at%20the%20Jayadev%20Bhawan%20on%20this%20occasion%20at%207%20pm%20on%20March%205%2C%20I%20request%20you%20to%20attend%20the%20programme%20as%20a%20special%20guest.%20Your%20graceful%20presence%20will%20dignify%20the%20programme%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20letter%20from%20Chief%20Minister%20Majhi%20to%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20whose%20party%20has%20termed%20the%20invitation%20as%20mere%20%26quot%3Bformality%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20political%20controversy%20deepened%2C%20a%20statue%20of%20Biju%20Patnaik%20was%20vandalised%20last%20evening%20in%20Cuttack.%20A%20case%20was%20registered%20and%20a%20new%20statue%20was%20installed%20within%20hours%20of%20the%20vandalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741157880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ft534q6fo_biju-patnaik-ndtv-_625x300_05_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-biju-patnaik-has-become-latest-bjp-vs-opposition-flashpoint-in-odisha-7852180%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20a%20hundred%20years%20after%20his%20birth%2C%20the%20legendary%20Odisha%20politician%20Biju%20Patnaik's%20birthday%20has%20become%20a%20political%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-biju-patnaik-has-become-latest-bjp-vs-opposition-flashpoint-in-odisha-7852180%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Transcript%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20speech%20to%20a%20joint%20session%20of%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741157533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118727964%2Cimgsize-854935.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftranscript-of-pre