%20People%20Trump%20Mentioned%20In%20His%20Address%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVolodymyr%20Zelensky%20-%20Ukrainian%20President%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20read%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20letter%26quot%3B%20from%20Zelensky%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20team%20and%20I%20stand%20ready%20to%20work%20under%20President%20Trump's%20strong%20leadership%20to%20get%20a%20peace%20that%20lasts.%26quot%3B%20Trump%20claimed%20Russia%20was%20also%20showing%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20signals%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20were%20ready%20for%20peace%2C%20suggesting%20a%20new%20diplomatic%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMelania%20Trump%20-%20First%20Lady%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20praised%20Melania's%20work%20in%20foster%20care%20and%20her%20advocacy%20for%20online%20safety%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BTake%20It%20Down%26quot%3B%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElon%20Musk%20-%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20showered%20praise%20on%20Musk%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%20and%20was%20present%20in%20the%20gallery.%20%26quot%3BElon%2C%20you%20are%20working%20very%20hard...%20he%20didn't%20need%20this...%20even%20this%20side%20(Democrats)%20appreciates%20this%2C%20they%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20admit%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKash%20Patel%20-%20FBI%20Director%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20highlighted%20Kash%20Patel's%20appointment%20as%20the%20new%20FBI%20director%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20politicisation%20at%20the%20FBI.%26quot%3B%20Trump%20also%20made%20a%20major%20announcement%2C%20revealing%20that%20Mohammad%20Sharifullah%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20top%20terrorist%20responsible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20deadly%20suicide%20bombing%20during%20the%202021%20Afghanistan%20withdrawal%2C%20had%20been%20apprehended%20by%20the%20FBI.%3