ppable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trump%20in%20a%20speech%20lasting%20over%20one%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%2C%20which%20beat%20Bill%20Clinton's%20record%20for%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20speech%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20line%20got%20loud%20applause%20from%20Republican%20Party%20members%2C%20including%20on%20two%20occasions%20when%20Trump%20singled%20out%20SpaceX%20and%20Tesla%20tycoon%20Musk%2C%20who%20stood%20up%20to%20salute%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20protests%20also%20began%20within%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Democratic%20congressman%2C%20Al%20Green%2C%20was%20ejected%20because%20he%20refused%20to%20stop%20heckling%20Trump%20over%20healthcare%20programs%2C%20and%20shaking%20his%20walking%20stick%20at%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Democrats%20silently%20held%20up%20placards%20including%20%26quot%3BFalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMusk%20steals%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20lie!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20at%20one%20moment%2C%20numerous%20Democrats%20yelled%20%26quot%3BJanuary%206!%26quot%3B%20at%20Trump%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20supporters'%20violent%20attack%20on%20the%20Capitol%20in%202021%20after%20he%20refused%20to%20concede%20his%20election%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20president%20was%20undeterred%2C%20hailing%20his%20first%20six%20weeks%20and%20vowing%20to%20press%20on%20with%20his%20polarizing%20bid%20to%20reshape%20the%20US%20government%20and%20end%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20--%20whatever%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReality%20TV%20style%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20reverted%20to%20his%20tried-and-tested%20reality%20TV%20instincts.%20At%20one%20point%20he%20called%20attention%20to%20a%20boy%20with%20brain%20cancer%20who%20--%20in%20front%20of%20Congress%20--%20was%20handed%20an%20official%20ID%20by%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Secret%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20what%20mostly%20sounded%20like%20a%20campaign%20speech%20rather%20than%20an%20address%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20Trump%20made%20no%20attempt%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20opponents%20and%20at%20times%20mocked%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20cheers%20of%20%26quot%3BUSA%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTrump%2C%20Trump%2C%20Trump%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20proclaimed%20that%20his%20culture%20war%20on%20diversity%20programs%20and%20transgender%20rights%20meant%20%26quot%3Bour%20country%20will%20be%20woke%20no%20longer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20resolve%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20catastrophe%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20inheriting%20the%20strongest%20developed%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20from%20his%20Democratic%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20defended%20his%20disruptive%20economic%20moves%20--%20even%20as%20the%20trade%20war%20he%20launched%20against%20Canada%2C%20China%20and%20Mexico%20is%20prompting%20jitters%20on%20world%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20ripped%20off%20for%20decades%20by%20nearly%20every%20country%20on%20earth%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20torrent%20of%20warnings%20that%20tariffs%20will%20badly%20hurt%20US%20exporters%2C%20including%20politically%20powerful%20farmers%2C%20he%20conceded%20they%20would%20bring%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20disturbance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20enumerating%20a%20series%20of%20murders%20committed%20by%20migrants%2C%20Trump%20got%20big%20applause%20when%20he%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bwage%20war%26quot%3B%20on%20Mexican%20drug%20cartels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%20before%20he%20had%20finished%2C%20dozens%20of%20Democrats%20had%20already%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuest%20for%20power%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20pushing%20to%20extend%20presidential%20power%20to%20its%20limits%2C%20with%20the%20popular%20vote%20behind%20him%20and%20a%20Republican-controlled%20House%20and%20Senate%20doing%20his%20bidding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAided%20by%20Musk%2C%20Trump%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20the%20federal%20bureaucracy%2C%20firing%20thousands%20of%20workers%2C%20shuttering%20entire%20agencies%20and%20decimating%20foreign%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20days%20of%20rule%20by%20unelected%20bureaucrats%20are%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20early%20signs%20in%20the%20polls%20that%20Trump's%20sweeping%20cuts%20and%20his%20failure%20to%20tackle%20inflation%20are%20hitting%20his%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20also%20upending%20US%20foreign%20policy%20with%20his%20pivot%20to%20Moscow%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20has%20stunned%20Kyiv%20and%20allies%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20a%20televised%20row%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20with%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20Trump%20said%20Ukraine's%20leader%20had%20told%20him%20he%20was%20now%20ready%20for%20talks%20with%20Russia%20and%20a%20US%20minerals%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20received%20an%20important%20letter%20from%20President%20Zelensky%20of%20Ukraine.%20The%20letter%20reads%20(that)%20Ukraine%20is%20ready%20to%20come%20to%20the%20negotiating%20table%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20bring%20lasting%20peace%20closer%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20controversial%20vows%20on%20%26quot%3Btaking%20back%26quot%3B%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20and%20getting%20Greenland%20from%20Denmark%20by%20%26quot%3Bone%20way%20or%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20have%20so%20far%20struggled%20to%20counter%20Trump's%20flood-the-zone%20strategy%20and%20his%20hogging%20of%20the%20news%20cycle%20with%20constant%20press%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Democrats'%20rebuttal%20speech%2C%20Senator%20Elissa%20Slotkin%20aimed%20her%20sober%20address%20at%20middleclass%20Americans%2C%20calling%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20%26quot%3Breckless%26quot%3B%20at%20home%20and%20giving%20up%20on%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20leadership%26quot%3B%20ab